<InftyDocument version="2.5">
	<head>
		
	<texsetting wysiwyg="0"/><paper pagenumber="1" margin="20,20,20,25">A4</paper></head>
	
<body fontsize="12pt" fontface="ＭＳ Ｐ明朝">
<p>最小化: <mblock><munit italic="1">z</munit><munit>=</munit><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock></p>
<p>条件: <mblock><munit italic="1">g<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">j</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>)</munit><munit>=</munit><munit>0</munit><munit> </munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">j</munit><munit>=</munit><munit>1</munit><munit>,</munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">m</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock></p>
<p>この問題の解の必要条件は、<mblock><munit entity="1" italic="1">lambda</munit><munit>=</munit><munit>(</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">lambda<mlink type="rsub"><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit>,</munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><munit>,</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">lambda<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">m</munit></mlink></munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>を導入して、</p>
<p><mblock><munit entity="1" italic="1">phi</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>,</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">lambda</munit><munit>)</munit><munit>=</munit><munit italic="1">f</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>)</munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1" style="big">sum<mlink type="under"><munit italic="1">j</munit><munit>=</munit><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">m</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">lambda<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">j</munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">g<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">j</munit></mlink></munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>   (5.5)</p>
<p>として、</p>
<p><mblock><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit entity="1">partial</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">phi</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1">partial</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">i</munit></mlink></munit></mlink></munit><munit>=</munit><munit>0</munit><munit> </munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">i</munit><munit>=</munit><munit>1</munit><munit>,</munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">n</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>    (5.6)</p>
<p><mblock><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit entity="1">partial</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">phi</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1">partial</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">lambda<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">j</munit></mlink></munit></mlink></munit><munit>=</munit><munit>0</munit><munit> </munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">j</munit><munit>=</munit><munit>1</munit><munit>,</munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">m</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>    (5.7)</p>
<p>が成立することである。ここで導入した<mblock><munit entity="1" italic="1">lambda<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">j</munit></mlink></munit></mblock>をラグランジュ未定乗数という。</p>
<p/>
<p>証明：<mblock><munit italic="1">x</munit></mblock>は<mblock><munit italic="1">n</munit></mblock>次元であるが、<mblock><munit italic="1">m</munit></mblock>本の制約条件式(独立とする)があるので、値を任意に設定できる</p>
<p>独立変数の数は<mblock><munit italic="1">n</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">m</munit></mblock>個である。ここで、独立変数を<mblock><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">m</munit><munit>+</munit><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit>,</munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit></mblock>とする。解は等号制約条件を満たし、目的関数を極値にするから、その近傍での微分(そのうち独立なものは<mblock><munit italic="1">n</munit><munit entity="1">minus</munit><munit italic="1">m</munit></mblock>個)について以下が成立する。</p>
<p/>
<p><mblock><munit entity="1" style="big">sum<mlink type="under"><munit italic="1">i</munit><munit>=</munit><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">m</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit entity="1">partial</munit><munit italic="1">g<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">i</munit></mlink></munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1">partial</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">i</munit></mlink></munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">d</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">i</munit></mlink></munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1" style="big">sum<mlink type="under"><munit italic="1">i</munit><munit>=</munit><munit italic="1">m</munit><munit>+</munit><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit entity="1">partial</munit><munit italic="1">g<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">j</munit></mlink></munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1">partial</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">i</munit></mlink></munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">d</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">i</munit></mlink></munit><munit>=</munit><munit>0</munit><munit> </munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">j</munit><munit>=</munit><munit>1</munit><munit>,</munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">m</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>   (5.8) 定数の微分は0</p>
<p><mblock><munit entity="1" style="big">sum<mlink type="under"><munit italic="1">i</munit><munit>=</munit><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">m</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit entity="1">partial</munit><munit italic="1">f</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1">partial</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">i</munit></mlink></munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">d</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">i</munit></mlink></munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1" style="big">sum<mlink type="under"><munit italic="1">i</munit><munit>=</munit><munit italic="1">m</munit><munit>+</munit><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit entity="1">partial</munit><munit italic="1">f</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1">partial</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">i</munit></mlink></munit></mlink></munit><munit italic="1">d</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">i</munit></mlink></munit><munit>=</munit><munit>0</munit></mblock>               (5.9)</p>
<p>ここで5.8式の<mblock><munit italic="1">m</munit></mblock>本の各式に<mblock><munit entity="1" italic="1">lambda<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">j</munit></mlink></munit></mblock>を乗じて5.9式に加えると次の式を得る</p>
<p><mblock><munit entity="1" style="big">sum<mlink type="under"><munit italic="1">i</munit><munit>=</munit><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">m</munit></mlink></munit><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit entity="1">partial</munit><munit italic="1">f</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1">partial</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">i</munit></mlink></munit></mlink></munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1" style="big">sum<mlink type="under"><munit italic="1">j</munit><munit>=</munit><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">m</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">lambda<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">j</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit entity="1">partial</munit><munit italic="1">g<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">i</munit></mlink></munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1">partial</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">i</munit></mlink></munit></mlink></munit></melem></marray><munit italic="1">d</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">i</munit></mlink></munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1" style="big">sum<mlink type="under"><munit italic="1">i</munit><munit>=</munit><munit italic="1">m</munit><munit>+</munit><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit><marray type="parenthesis"><melem><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit entity="1">partial</munit><munit italic="1">f</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1">partial</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">i</munit></mlink></munit></mlink></munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1" style="big">sum<mlink type="under"><munit italic="1">j</munit><munit>=</munit><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">m</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">lambda<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">j</munit></mlink></munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit entity="1">partial</munit><munit italic="1">g<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">j</munit></mlink></munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1">partial</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">i</munit></mlink></munit></mlink></munit></melem></marray><munit italic="1">d</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">i</munit></mlink></munit><munit>=</munit><munit>0</munit></mblock>    (5.10)</p>
<p>今<mblock><munit entity="1" italic="1">lambda<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">j</munit></mlink></munit></mblock>を下式を満たすように決めれば、5.10式の第1項は0となる。</p>
<p><mblock><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit entity="1">partial</munit><munit italic="1">f</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1">partial</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">i</munit></mlink></munit></mlink></munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1" style="big">sum<mlink type="under"><munit italic="1">j</munit><munit>=</munit><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">m</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">lambda<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">j</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit entity="1">partial</munit><munit italic="1">g<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">j</munit></mlink></munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1">partial</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">i</munit></mlink></munit></mlink></munit><munit>=</munit><munit>0</munit><munit> </munit><munit> </munit><munit> </munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">i</munit><munit>=</munit><munit>1</munit><munit>,</munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">m</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>   (5.11)</p>
<p>ところで、<mblock><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">m</munit><munit>+</munit><munit>1</munit></mlink></munit><munit>,</munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">n</munit></mlink></munit></mblock>は任意の独立変数であるから、(5.10)式の第2項が恒等的に0であるためには下式が成立しなければならない。</p>
<p><mblock><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit entity="1">partial</munit><munit italic="1">f</munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1">partial</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">i</munit></mlink></munit></mlink></munit><munit>+</munit><munit entity="1" style="big">sum<mlink type="under"><munit italic="1">j</munit><munit>=</munit><munit>1</munit></mlink><mlink type="upper"><munit italic="1">m</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">lambda<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">j</munit></mlink></munit><munit entity="1">frac<mlink type="upper"><munit entity="1">partial</munit><munit italic="1">g<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">j</munit></mlink></munit></mlink><mlink type="under"><munit entity="1">partial</munit><munit italic="1">x<mlink type="rsub"><munit italic="1">i</munit></mlink></munit></mlink></munit><munit>=</munit><munit>0</munit><munit> </munit><munit> </munit><munit> </munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">i</munit><munit>=</munit><munit italic="1">m</munit><munit>+</munit><munit>1</munit><munit>,</munit><munit entity="1">cdots</munit><munit>,</munit><munit italic="1">n</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>  (5.12)</p>
<p>(5.11)式と(5.12)式は(5.6)式を意味している。また(5.7)式は制約条件そのものである。よって、解は(5.6)式と(5.7)式を満たす必要がある。</p>
<p>なお、(5.6)式と(5.7)式は関数<mblock><munit entity="1" italic="1">phi</munit><munit>(</munit><munit italic="1">x</munit><munit>,</munit><munit entity="1" italic="1">lambda</munit><munit>)</munit></mblock>を<mblock><munit italic="1">x</munit></mblock>と<mblock><munit entity="1" italic="1">lambda</munit></mblock>それぞれについて極値にする条件である。(5.6)式によって<mblock><munit entity="1" italic="1">phi</munit></mblock>を極値にする<mblock><munit italic="1">x</munit></mblock>を<mblock><munit entity="1" italic="1">lambda</munit></mblock>の関数として求め、(5.7)式によってその中で制約条件を満たすように<mblock><munit entity="1" italic="1">lambda</munit></mblock>を決めると考えてもよい。</p>
<p/></body></InftyDocument>
